reviews.review_text: One of the best shows of the year Really great show.  Saw the two at Philly just prior and this one and this cap center show was easily the best of the bunch.  Healy had the sound tweaked perfectly for the second set, it was a magical night.  Tremendous song selection too, Greatest Story, Uncle Johns, Comes a Time....always one of my absolute favorites.  I've suggested this one to Lemieux as a release, he agrees it's worthy, not sure if the quality in the vault is up to par for an official release.  This one and the Hartford show from May were the best of the year IMO.  The rainbow mickey mouse helped!
